                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9991" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1495</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">772 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务主导逻辑下的价值共创：长江云数智人产品的B2B营销探索之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Value Co-Creation Based on the Service-Dominant Logic: The B2B Marketing Process of Changjiang Cloud Digital Human Products</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">严晨峰，但昭杰，付子甜（通讯作者），熊子皓，蒋大可</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖北长江云新媒体集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新闻出版业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务主导逻辑下的价值共创；情境价值；B2B营销；高科技产品；数智人；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Value co-creation based on the service-dominant logic, Value-in-context, B2B marketing, High-tech products, Digital human</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">以数智人为代表的高科技产品在市场营销过程中，常常面临需求不确定、过程不确定和结果不确定等现实挑战，亟需企业制定有针对性的营销战略。对此，服务主导逻辑下的价值共创聚焦特定情境下的产品使用价值，强调企业与顾客之间的双向服务和可操作性资源整合，是指导企业有效应对市场不确定性挑战的可行思路之一。本案例以湖北长江云新媒体集团有限公司数智人产品B2B营销的实践探索为主线，描述了该公司面临客户需求不明确、技术路线不清晰、市场标准模糊等挑战时，通过引导客户共同参与需求诊断、产品开发与优化等关键活动，不断提升其数智人产品解决客户情境问题的能力，最终实现数智人产品B2B营销阶段性突破的过程。本案例旨在引导学生学习服务主导逻辑下的价值共创的基本概念和过程机制，进而培养学生基于价值共创理论体系、开展高科技产品B2B营销实践的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">High-tech products often face demand uncertainty, process uncertainty and outcome uncertainty in the marketing process, which urgently requires firms to develop marketing strategies to address the uncertainty issues. In this regard, the idea of value co-creation under the service-dominant logic, argues the importance of the focus on the value-in-context, the activation of mutual services and the integration of operant resources between firms and their customers. It is considered as one of the feasible logics to guide enterprises to effectively respond to the challenges of market uncertainty. In this case, we document the B2B marketing process of Changjiang Cloud’s digital human products. Specifically, we show that under the challenges of unclear customer demands, unclear technical roadmap and vague market standard, Changjiang Cloud continuously improves its digital human products’ value-in-context, by guiding the customers to participate in the key marketing activities such as demand diagnosis, product development and optimization, and ultimately achieves a breakthrough in the terms of B2B marketing. This case aims to guide students to learn the basic concepts and the typical process of value co-creation based on the service-dominant logic, and then cultivate students&#39; ability to carry out B2B marketing practice of high-tech products from the value co-creation perspective.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《营销管理》、《组织营销（B2B营销）》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务主导逻辑；价值共创</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
